  slug the-conservation-of-foreign-exchange-and-prevention-of-smuggling-activities-act-1974
  handle (1618)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Conservation of Foreign Exchange and Prevention of Smuggling Activities Act, 1974`
  actNumber (52)
  enactmentDate 1974-12-13
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/1618`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `विदेशी मुद्रा संरक्षण और तस्‍करी निवारण अधिनियम,1974`
  actYear (1974)
  ministry `Ministry of Finance`
  department `Department of Revenue`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for preventive detention in certain cases for the purposes of conservation and augmentation of Foreign Exchange and prevention of smuggling activities and for matters connected therewith.`
  enforcementDate 19-12-1974
  notification `19th December, 1974, vide notification No. G.S.R. 690(E), dated 16th December, 1974, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3 (i).`
